Package com.cutterapi.math

The com.cutterapi.math package contains all classes that do certain mathematical things, like calculating random variables and sorting arrays

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalculationMethod
    This class has the functionality to automatically generate a MathML or HTML based calculation method You need to use CutterAPIs own math methods to make use of this feature, or implement the addCalculationStep()-method and the add descriptionForLastStep-method into your own code.
    Random
    The Random-class contains methods for creating random numbers, strings and booleans.
    Sort
    This class contains several methods for sorting number- and text-arrays
